{"code":200,"message":"","data":{"id":"1706","movieId":"1703","title":"摩根费里曼之神的万物论","tag":"国家地理频道·纪录片","desc":"国家地理频道《The Story of God with Morgan Freeman》","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/the-story-of-dod.jpg","introduces":[{"type":1000,"text":"国家地理频道《The Story of God with Morgan Freeman》","image":""},{"type":1001,"text":"","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/the-story-of-dod01.jpg"},{"type":1000,"text":"这些永恒及普世的谜团，影响了世上所有拥有信仰的人。摩根在节目中走访许多地方，亲自感受一些重要的宗教体验。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"从耶路撒冷的哭墙、印度的菩提树，到美国的超级教会。他也自告奋勇，充当实验室白老鼠，检视尖端神经科学和宇宙学，跟传统宗教之间的关系。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"他也跟考古学家一起探索人类祖先佚失的古老宗教，如土耳其有万年历史的哥贝克力山丘废墟。","image":""},{"type":1000,"text":"人和神的关系是人类史上最重要的问题，本节目探讨了信仰对我们生活造成的影响。","image":""}],"videos":[{"id":"1714","title":"1、第一集：超越死亡","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/the-story-of-dod.jpg","playCount":"6","playNumber":1,"playNumberDesc":"第一集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d11226606\u0026cid\u003d18568901\u0026page\u003d1","videoUrl":""},{"id":"1715","title":"2、第二集：末日启示","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/the-story-of-dod.jpg","playCount":"6","playNumber":2,"playNumberDesc":"第二集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d11226606\u0026cid\u003d18568902\u0026page\u003d2","videoUrl":""},{"id":"1716","title":"3、第三集：神为何人","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/the-story-of-dod.jpg","playCount":"6","playNumber":3,"playNumberDesc":"第三集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid\u003d11226606\u0026cid\u003d18568897\u0026page\u003d3","videoUrl":""},{"id":"1717","title":"4、第四集：创世之说","image":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ruzhan123/Lion/master/json/api/image/the-story-of-dod.jpg","playCount":"6","playNumber":4,"playNumberDesc":"第四集","playWebUrl":"http://player.bili